title: SmartFTP Client Enterprise 9.0.2529.0 + x64 + patch - Crackingpa
description:
Description: 
SmartFTP Client Enterprise 9.0.2529.0 + x64 SmartFTP Client - a program for working with FTP, SFTP, WebDAV, S3, SSH, FTPS, can be used as a Terminal client. You can easily share files between the local computer and the server on the Internet. Of the features can be allocated support for working with multiple FTP connections, which means that you can copy files between two servers without your participation, FXP support in general is available. In the rest nothing is different from other similar programs, it has a nice interface, built-in viewer, there is no Russian support, but there are a lot of settings, site manager, you can save the session, in general, a good program. 

Developer: SmartSoft Ltd 
License: ShareWare 
Language: English 
Size: 59 MB 
OS: Windows 

How to Install: 
1). Instructions are included in ReadMe.txt if needed. 
2). Thats all, Done & enjoy
